
<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color"><em><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://tsukinomayu.com/mead-gundam/" target="_blank">Mead Gundam</a></em> is a 321-page book featuring design drawings, concept sketches, and notes &amp; annotations by the late Syd Mead pertaining to his work on&nbsp;<em>Turn A Gundam</em>. Below is a translation of an introduction by Director Yoshiyuki Tomino.</p>



<div data-carousel-extra='{"blog_id":96907500,"permalink":"https:\/\/tsukinomayu.com\/2023\/06\/10\/an-introduction-by-yoshiyuki-tomino-for-mead-gundam\/"}'  class="wp-block-jetpack-tiled-gallery aligncenter is-style-rectangular"><div class="tiled-gallery__gallery"><div class="tiled-gallery__row"><div class="tiled-gallery__col" style="flex-basis:54.41365%"><figure class="tiled-gallery__item"><img data-attachment-id="9932" data-permalink="https://tsukinomayu.com/2023/06/10/an-introduction-by-yoshiyuki-tomino-for-mead-gundam/untitled-1-5/" data-orig-file="https://turnafeezy.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/untitled-1.jpg" data-orig-size="658,778" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="untitled-1" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://turnafeezy.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/untitled-1.jpg?w=254" data-large-file="https://turnafeezy.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/untitled-1.jpg?w=658" data-attachment-id="9932" data-permalink="https://tsukinomayu.com/2023/06/10/an-introduction-by-yoshiyuki-tomino-for-mead-gundam/untitled-1-5/" data-orig-file="https://turnafeezy.files.wordpress.com/2023/06/untitled-1.jpg" data-orig-size="658,778" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&